Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Oblasti* koje su pogođene poplavama su jako oštećene. (*Regions* affected by floods are heavily damaged.)
2. Predmet moje doktorske teze je *oblast* kvantne mehanike. (The subject of my doctoral thesis is the *field* of quantum mechanics.)
3. Ovaj hotel se nalazi u *oblasti* s prekrasnim pogledom na more. (This hotel is located in a *region* with a beautiful sea view.)
4. Sve *oblasti* medicine su mi jednako interesantne, ali najviše volim pedijatriju. (All *branches* of medicine are equally interesting to me, but I love pediatrics the most.)
5. *Oblast* koju pokriva ovaj sajt je tehnologija i inovacije. (The *field* covered by this website is technology and innovation.)
6. U ovoj *oblasti* ima mnogo nezaposlenih ljudi. (There are many unemployed people in this *region*.)
7. *Oblast* umetnosti mi je posebno draga, volim da posećujem izložbe i koncerte. (The *field* of art is especially dear to me, I like to visit exhibitions and concerts.)

I hope these examples help!